  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Ugandans Obtain Vital Health Services</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Uganda, vital healthcare for vulnerable people is often compromised by corruption. Life-saving medications go missing, funds to pay nurses disappear and patients are forced to pay bribes to save the lives of their loved ones. We created the Citizen Action Platform (CAP) as a means for patients to report and eliminate the maltreatment they confront. Now, people are able to stand-up to injustice and improve their communities through a simple text message.</narrative>
  </description>
